        created outside a function


Operators : 

    1) Arithematic Operators : 

            ex : +,-,/,*,%

    2) Relational Operators : 

            ex : ==, !=, >, <, >=, <=

        ex : 5 + 4 * 9 % ( 3 + 1 ) / 6 - 1

    3) Assignment Operators : 

            ex : =, +=, -=, *=, /=, %=

    4) Logical Operators : 

            ex : And, Or, Not 

    Logical Operators : 

        And gate : 
        A      B     A and B 
        T      T        T 
        T      F        F 
        F      T        F 
        F      F        F 

        Or gate :
        A      B    A or B 
        T      T      T 
        T      F      T 
        F      T      T 
        F      F      F 

        Not :

        A    Not A 
        T     F 
        F     T 
Not(Not(T))   T 



    






